name: Bird Above School
description:
Bahasa Indonesia
Klik dengan mouse di mana saja untuk memainkan game nya maka burung akan terbang ke atas dan hindari halangan berupa beton serta raihlah score sebanyak-banyak nya dan selamat bermain!

English
Click with the mouse anywhere to play the game, the birds will fly up and avoid obstacles in the form of concrete and get as much score as possible and enjoy playing!

Game DeveloperDEANDRA PUJI AMELIASMK Negeri 9 Malang
